Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.87,0:00:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.64,0:00:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.09,0:00:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.19,0:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.86,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.50,0:00:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.54,0:00:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.46,0:01:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重毒鞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當個好孩子 不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了!\N左側重鑽機駕駛艙 射擊預備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓...數量增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險!\N超重飛彈!全部發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等..怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點1559點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.58,0:02:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法使用超重壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影座艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢射擊預備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能量到達臨界值!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神...被解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八話超重戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為...為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當在合神中時\N絕對要遵從斗牙的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個人任意的行動\N將會使全體人員陷入險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好自律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我也知道啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!你根本不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在今天戰鬥中\N害超重神陷入危機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為某人被敵人嚇得半死\N就拼命亂發射飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有嚇得半死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.84,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那個時候還不是一樣\N錯失了出拳的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算替自己的失誤開罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把責任歸咎在我的操控上面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳磨磨蹭蹭的\N我才出手幫妳的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該感激我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次不管怎麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司還是沒什麼立場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.16,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不管是考慮\N攻擊力或重力子點數上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.27,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起飛彈 在當時\N最有效的攻擊仍然是壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算敵人分離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拳頭的破壞力下\N仍足以貫穿目標的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是可以擊敗對方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 是英司少爺他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,判斷錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不考慮太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你想讓訓練加倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是受到敵人攻擊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不只是第二發拳擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連新月鏢都無法使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司的潛力\N並不如大家想像的那麼低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.21,0:05:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了!斗牙是合神後\N超重神的頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔任手腳的我們\N要是沒有聽從頭腦指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任意行動的話\N不就錯失獲勝機會了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手腳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是腳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼態度呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也稍微有點女人樣吧\N電鑽女!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還敢說你這個腳丫男!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電鑽女...\N腳丫男...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳丫男!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手指部分的板金剝落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重鑽機的機體也歪七扭八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕累累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家昨晚才通宵打蠟的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重機組跟超重皇組合...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是"合神"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,針對這些機體使用的\N驅動機系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及制御系統上面的\N高科技分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.01,0:06:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在已進行到第4級的階段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如同您所見到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重機組跟EFA所使用的\N戰鬥用機械有著完全不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,複數構造發電機組\N以及驅動系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 這些對一般的\N飛行器、戰車而言並不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了合神的\N輔助動力跟驅動系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.03,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此那裡並沒有可以讓超重神\N產生高輸出動力的技術存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不談裝甲的材質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.94,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,構造上而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.87,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重機組不過是\N超重神的手腳罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能算是個零件組而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們製造出\N跟超重機組完全一樣的機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也完全打不贏外星異種的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照手上握有的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以38比1的比例成功重現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然就在這架超重皇上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼關於這架機體\N我們現在了解了多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過前些日子收到了\N很有意思的測量資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.81,0:07:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神進行戰鬥的範圍區內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.02,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀測到平時不可能發生的\N重力值急劇變化現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力?...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是牛頓的蘋果定律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神中絕對要遵從斗牙的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個人任意的行動\N將會使全體人員陷入險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳丫男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東東啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!我也一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.69,0:08:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用 斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生緊急狀況...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重機組的停機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被士兵級的外星異種入侵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人出現在城內?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有搞錯!\N是想叫我光溜溜的去作戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武裝女僕班立刻前往停機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請動員所有人員\N集中抵抗外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了!欠打的是外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡量不要損傷到城堡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的成員們\N跟武裝女僕班合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.99,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各個擊破城內的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 趴下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情大條了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有個萬一\N我們也得加入戰鬥才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准牠們踏進這個司令室一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城內竟然出現敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這座城堡的所在位置\N已經被對方知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.57,0:10:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不過是在白天交戰的外星異種\N有一部份在機庫裡再生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠的增殖速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘快掃除機庫內的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露 呼叫斗牙他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵城堡內的\N外星異種本體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經控制了超重機組的停機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎要第一優先\N徹底、迅速的清除掉所有在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.92,0:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通往超重皇停機庫路線內\N出現的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒辦法聯絡到英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊有什麼消息嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!他不在那邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用G呼叫也沒有回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種緊急的時刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇 啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...及時趕到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟連線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子!你在那裡幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然對我大叫啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不行的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給我下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能把現在在這個基地\N的外星異種全部消滅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以你跟超重皇的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以英司的能力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然!我當然行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司我們所有人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟這座城堡的命運\N就都交給你跟超重皇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對著那個\N巨大菱形的東西集中攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在牠羽化前打倒牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙\N我來當你們的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文敵人的行動很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇在停機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟被認為是主體的戰士級\N外星異種交戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵級的外星異種\N應該正趕往支援主體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.29,0:13:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等...你說超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在英司正在駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量太大了\N實在不好控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且操縱起來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙一直在搞這種\N累死人的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又變大了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像陷入危機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺請您回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺\N去司令室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意不賴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你整成這副德性\N這是回敬你的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有效?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 從那裡撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.69,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算對著毀滅者級\N外星異種反覆攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也無法造成牠的損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我撤退...\N我能撤到哪裡去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.73,0:17:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣!\N先把能打倒這傢伙的方法告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將手放在手臂握把前端的\N超重天球體上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等候桑德曼的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!絕對不可以這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有重力子的力量\N是無法打倒牠們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會消滅這傢伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說我也都上場啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工學型態時的超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會對搭乘者的肉體\N造成相當大的負擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦!看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那、那到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用工學型態...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又沒有進行合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什會那麼的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是超重皇\N實行重力子能量循環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己發揮\N原有力量的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實行工學型態時的超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.37,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會呼應操縱者本身\N所擁有的G因子而成為一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且在同一時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇的機體周圍\N會形成重力子力場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.01,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並誘發裝備在機體上武器的潛能\N產生大幅度的提升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給予其壓倒性的破壞力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.61,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會給予操縱者的肉體\N帶來無比的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼所謂臨界點又是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是超重機組可以抵擋\N重力子能量循環的界限值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而超重皇本身的臨界點......\N不存在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也該結束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟出一些不可燃燒的垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人的身體卻會有界限啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.69,0:21:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.30,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.30,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.56,0:22:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.69,0:22:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.93,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.84,0:22:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.11,0:22:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.55,0:22:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.43,0:22:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司讓我告訴你\N你所不知道的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.00,0:22:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐請注意\N不要在城內發生不正常關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.97,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出\N"遙遠的擁抱"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.81,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週也將照料各位的和平!